&lt;h3 id=&#34;指纹解决方案（通过替换-CredentialEnrollmentManager-exe-解锁）&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#指纹解决方案（通过替换-CredentialEnrollmentManager-exe-解锁）&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;指纹解决方案（通过替换 CredentialEnrollmentManager.exe 解锁）&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;指纹解决方案（通过替换 CredentialEnrollmentManager.exe 解锁）&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;参考 给 Windows Server 2022 配置 Windows Hello 指纹解锁 [ &lt;a href=&#34;https://afa31148-4a8c-4113-a92f-72626cd2a27b.x.wtf/2021/fingerprint-unlocking-for-windows-server-2022/&#34;&gt;https://afa31148-4a8c-4113-a92f-72626cd2a27b.x.wtf/2021/fingerprint-unlocking-for-windows-server-2022/&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;
